{"tid":466821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國駐港澳總領事館有可疑物品 警穿保護衣搜索","createTime":"2017-11-13T02:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T02:43:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"89c796ba6e8e8cc09e6ddef2993f5e8009a708ce","tid":466821,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510539330_5c16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510539330_5c16.jpg&h=79b069d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上9時許，中環花園道美國駐港澳總領事館，懷疑被放置可疑物品，多部消防車及救護車到場戒備，大批警員到場調查，有警員戴上防毒面罩，亦有警員穿上保護衣、雙手捧著印有「感染性物質」的盒子進入領事館範圍內搜查。大批市民在現場附近圍觀。現場消息指，領館職員早上接到一封帶有白色粉末的信封。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510538815_cc54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510538815_cc54.jpg&h=7aaf6815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171113/57451898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57451898&d=Xs2FPd0dkpmkrhVj0JzCg8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=959d7f67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57451898&h=7a359fee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171113/57451898</a>"},{"pid":"e88b45bf3d69a45c79888b4613533af581486310","tid":466821,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d266bc0256f6795418a03d40ae7facd326e8b2","tid":466821,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:43